channel.title: Webclient help
channel.description: Hello, I've .jar my client. I tested it and it opens and auto downloads my cache then loads to login screen without a problem. But, I've tried making a webclient with the code below with the client that works that I uploaded to dropbox. But the webclient just says it can't DL my cache... I really don't understand it but maybe someone could look at it over TV and help me? Or just tell me what I did wrong. Thanks. [code]<center> <applet name="server name here" width="765" height="503" archive="client link" code="client.class"> <param name="java_arguments" value="-Xmx1024m"/> </applet></center>[/code]
